'aYKH Y'yYB B'aPhV 'aDNY 'aTh-BTh-TShYVN HShLYK MShMYM 'aUrTSh ThPh'aUrTh YShUr'aL VL'a-ZKUr HDM-UrGLYV BYVM 'aPhV.
